/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NME-KNEECAP-PLAYLIST-STORY-HERO-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NME-KNEECAP-PLAYLIST-STORY-HERO-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NME-KNEECAP-PLAYLIST-STORY-HERO-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NME-KNEECAP-PLAYLIST-STORY-HERO-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NME-KNEECAP-PLAYLIST-STORY-HERO-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NME-KNEECAP-PLAYLIST-STORY-HERO-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>上个月讨论了他们不参加抵制<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/the-great-escape">《大逃亡》</a>的原因。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-kneecap-interview-fine-art-3761722">封面上的膝盖骨：给和平、抗议和派对一个机会</a></strong></li></ul><p>超过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/great-escape-2024-boycott-barclays-gaza-palestine-bands-explain-interview-3756631">100 名艺术家因巴克莱银行的赞助而退出布莱顿音乐节</a>，巴克莱银行被指控与武装以色列的公司存在财务关系。然而，该银行声称其“是根据客户指示或要求进行上市公司股票交易”。</p><p>爱尔兰说唱三人组的决定在网上引起了一些争议，因为他们一直反对以色列对加沙的“占领和种族灭绝”。</p><p>他们帮助为巴勒斯坦阿伊达难民营的志愿者健身房筹集了近 10 万英镑，并通过社交媒体公开谈论了此事，并在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/jimmy-fallon"><em>吉米·法伦</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kneecap-make-explosive-us-tv-debut-on-jimmy-fallon-3599087">高调亮相</a><em>《今夜秀》</em>后分享了一条信息。他们还因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kneecap-perform-grian-chatten-collab-better-way-to-live-and-talk-controversy-on-irelands-late-late-show-3592326">无视爱尔兰公共广播公司 RTÉ 不佩戴亲巴勒斯坦徽章的要求而成为头条新闻。</a></p><p>在发现美国军方支持该节日后，Kneecap 确实参与了对<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/sxsw-festival">SXSW</a>的抵制（在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-accuse-uk-government-of-silencing-them-by-last-minute-funding-block-3585062">英国政府撤回了艺术资助以让他们到达那里</a>之后；导致了一场法律诉讼）。最终，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/irish-bands-sxsw-boycott-statement-palestine-radar-3601576">每部爱尔兰剧都退出了</a>。</p><p>现在，Kneecap在最新一期 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-kneecap-interview-fine-art-3761722">的NME封面</a></em>中评论了他们为什么仍然参加The Great Escape。 </p><figure id="attachment_3761116" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761116" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761116" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700.jpg" alt="NME (2024) 封面上的膝盖，摄影：Joseph Bishop" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NME-COVER-KNEECAP-CREDIT-JOSEPH-BISHOP@2160x2700-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761116" class="wp-caption-text"> NME 封面上的膝盖骨。图片来源：NME 的 Joseph Bishop</figcaption></figure><p> “如果你的收入取决于此生，并且你是一支巡演乐队，那么一切都以某种方式与这些公司之一联系在一起，”成员莫格莱·巴普 (Móglaí Bap) 说道。 “理想情况下，如果我们有钱，我们就会抵制一切，坐在家里整天发推文。”</p><p>与此同时，乐队成员莫·查拉 (Mo Chara) 辩称“SXSW 显然是完全不同的事情”，并补充道：“那是军队赞助的，你知道我的意思吗？”</p><p>在详细阐述他们演奏《大逃亡》的决定时，查拉说：“我们也遇到过巴勒斯坦人，他们也表示，他们认为艺术家的负担也不公平。他们完全同意：你去吧，你赚钱，你说你能做的。你愿意无缘无故地当烈士吗？如果你退出这个音乐节、赔钱、失去平台，没人会在意。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-ins